  <brief_title>Transfer From Methadone to Buprenorphine Maintenance Treatment Using Buprenorphine Patches</brief_title>
  <official_title>Transfer From Methadone to Buprenorphine Maintenance Treatment Using Buprenorphine Patches: A Study on Practicability With Patients Maintained With Daily Dosages Between 60mg and 100mg Methadone.</official_title>
